 cutoff energy of the spectra are also quite different. We will present\nthe results of our analysis, compare it with previous studies, and discuss the\nagreement of our results with the theory of wave-particle interaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2010 09:47:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Aug 2011 13:17:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
